parameters.query: SELECT setting_key, setting_value FROM global_settings WHERE setting_key IN ('exchange_rate_usd_jpy', 'exchange_rate_eur_jpy', 'exchange_rate_gbp_jpy', 'vat_rate_eu', 'vat_rate_uk', 'ioss_threshold', 'ebay_fee_percent', 'paypal_fee_percent')
SELECT id, sku, product_name, cost_price, weight_kg, hts_code, origin_country, listing_price, listing_currency, supplier_data FROM products_master WHERE id = ANY($1::uuid[])
UPDATE products_master SET pricing_data = pricing_data || $1::jsonb, updated_at = NOW() WHERE id = $2 RETURNING id, sku

options.queryParams: ={{ [JSON.stringify({ global_calc: $json.calculation, net_profit: $json.net_profit, profit_margin: $json.profit_margin, recommended_price: $json.recommended_price, calculated_at: new Date().toISOString() }), $json.id] }}
